# 🚀 **ProJobHub**

A modern, full-featured job portal built with **React**, **TypeScript**, and **Supabase** — by **Krish Yadav**.

---

## 📋 **Project Overview**

ProJobHub helps job seekers find opportunities and employers post jobs with ease. Powered by cutting-edge technologies and sleek design.

---

## 🔐 **Authentication & User Management**

* 🔑 **Supabase Auth** – Secure sign-up & login
* 👤 **User Profiles** – Manage personal information
* 🚫 **Protected Routes** – Access control for authenticated features

---

## 💼 **Job Management**

* 🔍 **Job Browsing** – Search and explore listings
* 🎯 **Advanced Filtering** – Role, location, salary, experience, etc.
* 🧾 **Job Details Modal** – Clean UI (e.g., `JobModal.tsx` with smooth close button)
* ➕ **Job Posting** – For logged-in employers

---

## 💬 **Real-time Messaging**

* 💬 **Live Chat** – Built with Supabase Realtime
* 👥 **Community Features** – Connect with others

---

## 🎨 **Modern UI/UX**

* 📱 **Responsive Design** – Works on all devices
* 💫 **Animations** – Smooth transitions & hover effects
* 🧊 **Glassmorphism** – Modern aesthetic
* 🌌 **Moving Background** – Dynamic visuals
* 🌗 **Dark/Light Mode** – Supports `next-themes`

---

## 🔍 **Smart Search & Filtering**

* 📝 **Keyword Search**
* 📍 **Location Filter** – Remote/Onsite
* 💰 **Salary Range** – Adjustable slider
* 📈 **Experience Level** – Junior → Senior
* ⏳ **Employment Type** – Full-time, part-time, contract, internship

---

## 🛠️ **Technology Stack**

### ⚛️ Frontend

* React 18 + Hooks
* TypeScript
* Vite ⚡
* Tailwind CSS 🎨
* shadcn/ui 🧩

### 🔙 Backend & DB

* Supabase – BaaS 🔐
* PostgreSQL – Relational DB 🗄️
* RLS – Row-Level Security 🛡️
* Real-time Subscriptions 🔔

### 🧰 Libraries

* React Router DOM – Routing
* Tanstack React Query – Data management
* React Hook Form – Form handling
* Lucide React – Icons ✨
* Recharts – Graphs & Charts 📊

---

## 📁 **Project Structure**

```bash
src/
├── components/
│   ├── ui/              # shadcn/ui components
│   ├── JobCard.tsx
│   ├── JobList.tsx
│   ├── JobModal.tsx
│   ├── JobSidebar.tsx
├── pages/
│   ├── Index.tsx
│   ├── Auth.tsx
│   ├── Profile.tsx
│   ├── Messages.tsx
│   ├── Hiring.tsx
├── hooks/
│   └── useAuth.tsx
├── services/
│   └── jobsService.ts
├── data/
│   └── jobs.ts
└── integrations/
    └── supabase/
```

---

## 🗄️ **Database Schema**

* 🧑 **profiles** – User info
* 💼 **jobs** – Job listings
* 💬 **messages** – Chat system

🔐 **Security Features**

* RLS policies
* Auto-profile creation
* Real-time updates

---

## 🎯 **Core Functionality**

* 🛠️ CRUD for jobs
* 📡 Real-time updates
* 📱 Smooth, responsive UX
* 🔁 Modern loading states
* ❌ Robust error handling

